message.raw:
The new sets/ directory structure with some examples.
Much more to come.
And documentation about the directory structure to be written
Basically each directory with a unique name (can't be other way)
There the .material scripts
and a directory with the name of the model
All the materials in a given .material script have to be Gazebo/ModelName/MaterialName

Much more models will come here (this is just a initial import)
